lead_paragraph: Captain Steve Smith raised a composed century to push Australia to a 22-run first innings lead before a storm brought tea early on day four of the second test against Pakistan on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Cricket-Captain Smith Scores Ton to Rain on Pakistan Parade
